Name: Cubicus
About the game: An addictive puzzle game with many challenging levels of varying difficulty. Cubicus has tons of unique blocks and levels, so complete them all! You have to go from beginning to end, solving interesting puzzles! Whether you will be able to go this way is up to you. Features of the game: - Many levels - Convenient management - Physics - Colorful graphics
